    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that stands out immediately as a carefully kept, highly attractive car. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep shine, crisp trim, and only the slightest signs of age if you look very closely. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and well preserved, with upholstery, surfaces, and controls showing minimal wear and giving the car a well-cared-for feel throughout. This is the kind of example a buyer can feel proud to own right away, whether for regular enjoyment, weekend use, or adding to a collection. Overall, it shows as a top-tier car that needs no excuses and should satisfy someone looking for one of the nicest examples available.",
