      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, first car, or handy runaround? This one isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward budget-friendly car with plenty of potential for the right buyer. Great chance to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune, and with a bit of TLC it could really serve someone well. If you want something honest, cheap to get into, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
