      "description": "Driver-grade project with strong enthusiast potential. This car shows its age cosmetically and needs attention, but it still presents as a worthwhile platform with a responsive powertrain, usable chassis, and plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around maintenance and sorting. A good candidate for a budget daily, weekend tinkering, or a build base\u2014priced to move for the next owner ready to put in the work.",
